# ==========================================
# MFE GLOBAL GITIGNORE (Sigma Protection)
# ==========================================

# 1. Global Dependencies (The '**/' is magic)
# Yeh command project ke kisi bhi kone mein node_modules ko block kar degi
**/node_modules/
**/npm-debug.log
**/yarn-error.log

# 2. Global Build & Output Folders
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.cache/

# 3. Environment Variables (Security)
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# 4. OS & Editor Junk
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# 5. Project Specific Root Files (Agar root level par koi build tools hain)
package-lock.json 
# (Note: Agar aap chahte hain ki versions exact lock rahein team ke liye, toh package-lock.json ko ignore MAT kijiye. Par agar akele dev kar rahe hain aur conflicts aa rahe hain, toh ignore kar sakte hain. Standard practice hai isko ignore NAHI karna.)